---
title: Family Day Build-Your-Own Burger Bar with Bacon, Goat Cheese, Cheddar, Mushrooms and Potato Coins
description: How do you make everyone in the family happy at dinnertime? Easy — a build-your-own burger bar! Choosy eaters will love the ketchup, cheddar cheese and creamy mustard-mayo sauce, while the more adventurous among you will be all over the sophisticated goat cheese, crisp baby gem lettuce, smoky bacon and sautéed mushrooms.

Protein Plus (50 g protein or more) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's protein amount.

